author: jdcasey
msg: Refactor the artifact-scanning logic from the realm manager and the plugin-artifact resolution logic in the plugin manager into two separate classes, one a component and one a static class, to allow the new PluginPrefixLoader to reuse some of both and create a lighter-weight approach to grabbing the PluginDescriptor for build-planning purposes...also avoids some needless error messages during build planning.
